{"tid":1780589,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"誠邀各方紳士上車，台灣團隊開發「同步率100%」互動式飛機杯集資計畫啟動","createTime":"2019-12-12T13:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T03:03:22.000Z","uid":75050,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"727de607ac8595cb34bc15a5bf31bc30b03c3a52","tid":1780589,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:06:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/94674/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F94674%2F%3F&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc%2FcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=66624190\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/94674/?</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/00-27.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F00-27.jpg%3F&h=99438933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n誠邀各方紳士上車，台灣團隊開發「同步率100%」互動式飛機杯集資計畫啟動<br />\n作者: ACGER編輯部 日期: 12/12/2019<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「國產互動飛機杯《A-GUI搖桿》集資計畫啟動，產品明年問世」</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/01-1.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F01-1.png%3F&h=bb7e35fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主打能與遊戲中的虛擬角色達到「同步率100%」的互動式飛機杯《A-GUI搖桿》於12/12日晚上9點在嘖嘖啟動集資計畫，《A-GUI搖桿》結合了人因科技與數位遊戲，透過物聯網的概念突破了次元的限制，將帶領玩家與遊戲中的角色做羞羞的事情，商品預計於2020年暑假開始出貨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/07.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F07.png%3F&h=185263f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/04-17.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F04-17.jpg%3F&h=7172094f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「尻尻」是眾多男性，解決生理需求的一種管道與途徑。<br />\n<br />\n有多少次，在「尻尻」的過程中，您微微的闔上了雙眼，任由電腦的音響發出令人心癢難耐的嬌喘，您的手臂隨著那頻率而穩定地做動，時快時慢，只為了達到與片中的女角心領神會。<br />\n<br />\n「A-GUI搖桿」讓您體驗與虛擬女角最直接的互動關係，無須大腦想像，開啟遊戲，連接裝置，讓我們用最習慣的方式放飛自我。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/02.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F02.png%3F&h=52c526bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n本次集資最主要的目的，就是為了籌備量產所需的「開模費用」，經過製作人的奔波走訪，各家模具廠商的報價也不盡相同，從150萬到250萬的區間都有，著實讓開發團隊傷透腦筋。<br />\n<br />\n畢竟團隊規模小(3個人而已)，從2016年開發至今一直都是處於燒錢的狀態，電路板開發、飛機杯外觀機構設計、遊戲美術、配音等等&hellip;.，儘管中間有出一些商品來販售，但是杯水車薪。<br />\n<br />\n到最後發現開模還要一兩百萬，其實在心理上壓力真的不小，但開發團隊仍然堅持下去，希望能帶給大家一個全新的體驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/03-17.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F03-17.jpg%3F&h=05eae0c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《A-GUI搖桿》集資計畫已於嘖嘖正式啟動，開發團隊期望透過集資計畫來籌措「開模費用」，進而開始量產商品，讓更多有需要的人可以找到屬於自己的幸福。<br />\n<br />\n集資項目包含「飛機杯本體」、「青梅竹馬是能幹的妹妹呦」、「韓老師的課後輔導」、「這樣的愛乃是天下無敵」等三款遊戲供玩家選購，還請大家多多支持！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/05.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F05.png%3F&h=36a44b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/06-11.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F06-11.jpg%3F&h=ee53ee5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想進一步了解募資計畫或是支持團隊的玩家們，可點選下列募資連結參考詳細情形。<br />\n<br />\n▌嘖嘖集資頁面：<a href=\"https://zecz.ec/2LMNiTX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzecz.ec%2F2LMNiTX&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc%2FcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=47a2c4a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://zecz.ec/2LMNiTX</a><br />\n▌FB粉絲專頁：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JpVB7E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JpVB7E&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc%2FcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=3b4021d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JpVB7E</a><br />\n▌推特：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IZpREU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IZpREU&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc%2FcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=30664f9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IZpREU</a>"},{"pid":"d9417c47b0f68e50eac28aa2b5dccd2be0f33c82","tid":1780589,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:08:09.000Z","msg":"cm3d唔係已經有呢種飛機杯啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524a49163daafb41f4876a2df0439835495185db","tid":1780589,"uid":49336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:08:44.000Z","msg":"話說六道仙人去咗邊"},{"pid":"2cd33b3b3e7172a1b9997803696caec7ab08481f","tid":1780589,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9417c47b0f68e50eac28aa2b5dccd2be0f33c82","tid":1780589,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:08:09.000Z","msg":"cm3d唔係已經有呢種飛機杯啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"呢隻好似係專用型，for呢隻game"},{"pid":"96dba557c3a7b919d61c87e5399791a14023ee95","tid":1780589,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T01:12:37.000Z","msg":"5G打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69f339d74e2a6516fe76ab81f622e70b72d0f10","tid":1780589,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"感覺用完會變太監<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b35653ebc8406b1e4a7e00cb58cbfd95ebc403d","tid":1780589,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"打飛機就係想快快手搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要開住隻game慢慢磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal